HEADWORD: Sundrops
<hw>Sun"drops`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Sun</ets> +
<ets>drop</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Any one of the several
species of <gen>Kneiffia</gen>, esp. <spn>Kneiffia fruticosa</spn> (syn.
<spn>Oenothera fruticosa</spn>), of the Evening-primrose family, having
flowers that open by daylight.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

